{"tid":891460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局總裁陳德霖：樓市跌逾10%將出現負資產","createTime":"2018-11-06T06:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:33:06.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"089bbb19e5677ab1f12e414d6b809ebc757560c2","tid":891460,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181106/20539341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539341&d=uhKk4%2BaM5TcFbhkeqGl3Ib%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a8556f0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539341&h=7f46cfa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181106/20539341</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181106/large/1105tam0104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1105tam0104.jpg&h=dd8d3aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳德霖昨出席立法會財經事務委員會會議上回應樓市問題。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港樓市交投放緩、劈價潮湧現，樓價連番下跌。金管局總裁陳德霖，坦言倘樓價下調多於一成，普遍使用發展商高成數按揭者，便會出現負資產。<br />\n記者：黃珮琳<br />\n<br />\n港股輾轉下跌，削弱市民投資信心，樓價從今年8月起回落。根據差餉物業估價署數據，今年第三季樓價累計下跌1.5%，同期中原城市領先指數亦累跌2.6%，9月份住宅交投量更一度跌至3,500宗，為20個月新低。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員葉劉淑儀憂慮負資產激增，或會於發展商提供的高成數按揭集中爆發，陳德霖坦言，倘樓價下調多於一成，普遍使用發展商高成數按揭者，便會出現負資產。"},{"pid":"e7096d83e4a6f79720a5dab39f4f7ee0fc58a994","tid":891460,"uid":36178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"呼吸plan變斷氣plan"},{"pid":"50f01e62dba12e7365547ab5cac17306c00466a5","tid":891460,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成千萬年薪賣港狗，教你：1+1等於2！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3577defa721c4f8b297d545a9660d58911b1c539","tid":891460,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"放心，跌10%我都買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c9dcfde3f5f33e15a725935aae546ea7f0ce14","tid":891460,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"33c75329008c657758ad1eeaceee09a933ca0970","tid":891460,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"跌一成就負資產嗰啲，根本就係買唔起而夾硬上呼吸plan嘅on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc1ed558133c4f54a385e7606245b2e83937e69","tid":891460,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"負資產+加息 =換唔到樓套現<br />\n唔使失業都會死一大堆"},{"pid":"ae4e6d8b8142df4a1596496212261e2bb4dc454b","tid":891460,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"入定棺材股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a84c7f281d0ebb9a95a26161b8356e9d6dbe6b7","tid":891460,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:33:06.000Z","msg":"人哋計好數先買驚閪"}]}